      <h1>About College of Letters &amp; Science</h1> 
      <p>The College of Letters &amp; Science teaches students to <strong>make a good living and lead a good life.</strong> We are the largest academic unit at <abbr title="University of Wisconsin at Madison">UW-Madison</abbr> and the <a href="http://www.ls.wisc.edu/about-overview.html" target="_blank">heart of this great institution</a>. L&amp;S is home to more than 800 faculty, 22,000 undergraduate and graduate students and 190,000 living alumni.</p> 
